OL,3,C'My family was ripped away from me':
OL,4,CMan orphaned by infected blood scandal
OL,6,FA man who lost his entire family aged
OL,7,Fthree as a result of the infected
OL,8,Fblood scandal says he is desperately
OL,9,Flooking for some kind of closure from
OL,10,Fthe report.
OL,12,FSam Rushby became an orphan at the age
OL,13,Fof three, when his mother, father and
OL,14,Fsister all died after being affected
OL,15,Fby contaminated blood.
OL,17,FHis haemophiliac father Gary had
OL,18,Freceived contaminated Factor 8, a
OL,19,Fclotting agent derived from blood
OL,20,Fplasma, and had no idea it made him
OL,21,FHIV positive.
