OL,3,C'My family was ripped away from me':
OL,4,CMan orphaned by infected blood scandal
OL,6,FHe then unknowingly passed it to his
OL,7,Fwife Lesley and their new baby girl
OL,8,FAbbey.
OL,10,FThe youngster died aged just four-
OL,11,Fmonths-old, while her 23-year-old
OL,12,Fmother Lesley died in 1994, followed
OL,13,Fby Gary in 1995 at the age of 34.
OL,15,FAll had AIDS related conditions.
OL,17,F"Basically my whole family were torn
OL,18,Faway from me," he said.
