OL,3,C'My family was ripped away from me':
OL,4,CMan orphaned by infected blood scandal
OL,6,F"(Dad) watched his four-month-old
OL,7,Fdaughter die, then he watched his wife
OL,8,Fdie and he knew he was going to die.
OL,9,FIt's just horrific."
OL,11,FNow, decades later, Sam is calling on
OL,12,Fthe government to pay compensation to
OL,13,Fall those whose lives have been
OL,14,Fblighted by what has been described as
OL,15,Fthe biggest treatment disaster in NHS
OL,16,Fhistory.
OL,18,F"I feel so, so guilty that my sister
OL,19,Fdied while I survived. But one thing I
OL,20,Fknow is I'm here now to get justice
OL,21,Ffor them," he added.
