OL,3,C'My family was ripped away from me':
OL,4,CMan orphaned by infected blood scandal
OL,6,FThirty thousand people were infected
OL,7,Fwith HIV and Hepatitis C, including
OL,8,F380 children - 3,000 have died.
OL,10,F"People are dying every day, what are
OL,11,Fthey waiting for," he says, accusing
OL,12,Fministers of dragging their feet on
OL,13,Fpayouts that could amount to #40
OL,14,Fbillion before a general election.
OL,16,FA long-awaited report will be
OL,17,Fpublished on Monday 20 May following
OL,18,Fthe Infected Blood Inquiry which heard
OL,19,Fevidence from hundreds of witnesses
OL,20,Ffrom 2019 to 2023.
