OL,3,C'My family was ripped away from me':
OL,4,CMan orphaned by infected blood scandal
OL,6,FDrug addicts, sex workers and
OL,7,Falcoholics were among those regularly
OL,8,Fgiving blood, increasing the risk of
OL,9,Fthat supply being infected.
OL,11,FThe inquiry's heard allegations of a
OL,12,Fcover-up of the mistakes made,
OL,13,Fincluding the warnings that came from
OL,14,Fthe United States about the rising
OL,15,Frisk of infections.
OL,17,FSam has had thousands of signatures on
OL,18,Fa calling for compensation to be paid
OL,19,Fto those infected and those affected
OL,20,Fby the loss of family members.
