OL,3,C'My family was ripped away from me':
OL,4,CMan orphaned by infected blood scandal
OL,6,FSpeaking of those who continued to
OL,7,Fsupply Factor8 despite knowing the
OL,8,Frisks, he said: "I think they should
OL,9,Fbe in prison.
OL,11,F"If you or I did it, we'd be locked up
OL,12,Fso why is it okay for higher officials
OL,13,Fto get away with it?"
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the UK Government
OL,16,Fsaid: "This was an appalling tragedy
OL,17,Fthat never should have happened. We
OL,18,Fare clear that justice needs to be
OL,19,Fdone, and swiftly.
